  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Castillo Fuerte/Casa de Misericordia ~ Health &amp; Education Support</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to support the provision of education &amp;amp; nutrition services along with moral instruction in a safe space for children and staff at the Castillo Fuerte sites of Chorillos and La Victoria, among some of the most economically challenged areas of Lima, Peru. LWR support will also allow the NGO - Castillo Fuerte - to increase their financial stability through the search for and commitment of more long-term financial supporters. The project seeks 2 outcomes: 
1) Safe spaces for children and staff, provided through additional teacher training; maintenance of government-mandated adult to child ratios; continued provision of program activities &amp;amp; services to participant children 
2) Increased financial stability for NGO - Castillo Fuerte through the addition of more long-term financial supporters.</narrative>
  </description>
